main event: A round, white object was observed going straight up for 13 minutes in Walertown, S. Dakota.
interesting points: The sighting occurred under windy and hazy conditions., The observation was visual and lasted for 13 minutes., The object was described as a civilian round and white., The conclusion of the investigation was that the object was a balloon., The sighting was logged on a Project 10673 record card from Project Blue Book.
witness description: age 17, student from Los Angeles, California
